01:12:54.710 --> 01:12:59.429
He is not going to allow you any more time

01:12:59.630 --> 01:13:05.260
and that will be the time of complete
destruction of all the satanic forces.

01:13:05.461 --> 01:13:08.247
So that is the Ekadasha here. That
collects,

01:13:08.448 --> 01:13:12.909
because all these horrible gurus are here.
