01:13:13.110 --> 01:13:16.843
And this is one thing is to be understood

01:13:17.044 --> 01:13:19.829
that one should get rid of this very
easily.

01:13:20.030 --> 01:13:24.510
Now, these two children of Rama who
were born here,

01:13:24.710 --> 01:13:28.870
and they are endowed on the sun and
the moon.

01:13:29.070 --> 01:13:31.549
The sun and the moon both are here.

01:13:31.750 --> 01:13:36.101
And the sun became - as I told you -
Buddha ultimately here,

01:13:36.302 --> 01:13:41.933
and he became the - not ultimately -
the Mahavira, they are here.

01:13:42.134 --> 01:13:46.598
But when they were on this earth, Buddha
talked about non-violence,

01:13:46.799 --> 01:13:54.233
and people thought non-violence
to chickens, to bugs.

01:13:54.434 --> 01:13:58.537
These Mahavira people, these Jains, we have
got horrible community

01:13:58.738 --> 01:14:02.910
called Jains in India. And they believe
in vegetarianism to this extent

01:14:03.111 --> 01:14:07.928
that they get a Brahmin, pay him money
and put him in a hut

01:14:08.129 --> 01:14:13.007
and bring all the bugs of the village,
put those in the hut

01:14:13.208 --> 01:14:16.710
and the bugs live on that Brahmin.
Is a fact, even today they do it.

01:14:16.910 --> 01:14:21.403
And then they pay some money
to the Brahmin, because the bugs are fed.

01:14:21.604 --> 01:14:25.189
Now, you just tell me this kind
of a nonsensical vegetarianism.

01:14:25.390 --> 01:14:29.029
Am I going to give realisation to chickens?

01:14:29.230 --> 01:14:32.750
Just think of it. Or to the bugs or
to the earthworms?

01:14:32.950 --> 01:14:36.430
You are human beings, you should
eat a flesh

01:14:36.630 --> 01:14:40.192
which is not of a bigger animal than
yourself, because that’s horrid.

01:14:40.393 --> 01:14:44.430
But you can eat the flesh of the animals
which are smaller than you.

01:14:44.630 --> 01:14:48.590
There’s no harm in eating that - and this
kind of a nonsensical vegetarianism,

01:14:48.790 --> 01:14:52.531
“Don’t do any harm to the animals”, but
they don’t mind doing this.

01:14:52.732 --> 01:14:58.451
Jains are the greatest, they are, you see,
such - just like suckers.

01:14:58.652 --> 01:15:01.774
And they don’t mind killing people for
their money.

01:15:01.975 --> 01:15:08.063
They don’t mind going for - what you call -
shikars, in hunting and killing anything;

01:15:08.264 --> 01:15:15.190
but they will not eat a chicken or even
the garlic.

01:15:15.390 --> 01:15:21.141
Now, garlic, as you know, is very good
for the heart. But they don’t eat garlic.

01:15:21.342 --> 01:15:24.793
It’s very good for the heart, it’s very
good for people who have got

01:15:24.994 --> 01:15:28.029
a tendency towards hardening
of the arteries,

01:15:28.230 --> 01:15:32.309
when the circulation is a problem, it’s
very good to eat that, and for cold.

01:15:32.510 --> 01:15:35.545
Those people who suffer from cold, if they
regularly eat

01:15:35.746 --> 01:15:40.852
a fresh garlic thing in the night, brush
their teeth, they’ll be much better off.

01:15:41.053 --> 01:15:45.938
So, while talking about it I would say.
Now, these seven centres are here.

01:15:46.139 --> 01:15:52.507
Now, at the fontanel bone is the centre
of the heart.

01:15:52.708 --> 01:15:57.149
Now, just imagine, it is at the centre.
So, where do I exist?

01:15:57.350 --> 01:16:02.207
I mean, all of them are seven centres,
so I am just like a bubble.

01:16:02.408 --> 01:16:05.509
But if I am in your heart, I’m there.

01:16:05.710 --> 01:16:12.242
So, the key of Sahaja Yoga that you have
to recognise me.

01:16:12.443 --> 01:16:15.455
If you cannot recognise me you cannot
progress in Sahaja Yoga,

01:16:15.656 --> 01:16:19.149
I have to frankly admit it. Because
he’s already exposed me,

01:16:19.350 --> 01:16:21.587
I don’t tell this in my first lectures,

01:16:21.788 --> 01:16:24.869
but I have to say that “Please, now
recognise me.”

01:16:25.070 --> 01:16:28.030
As your Mother I would request you
to recognise me.

01:16:28.230 --> 01:16:31.819
And you don’t have to give me anything,
just take things from me.

01:16:32.020 --> 01:16:34.381
Just have it yourself. But recognise me.

01:16:34.582 --> 01:16:38.556
If you deny me then this won’t open,
this will be always covered.

01:16:38.757 --> 01:16:41.901
That’s why at the end when you say,
“Mother, give me my realisation.”

01:16:42.102 --> 01:16:44.510
Because I have come on this earth to give
you realisation.

01:16:44.710 --> 01:16:50.856
That’s my job. It’s one of the worst jobs
that one can have.

01:16:54.023 --> 01:16:58.291
Because it is so difficult with people:
to talk to them, to tell them about it,

01:16:58.492 --> 01:17:03.510
and they are all the time up in arms, they
are so aggressive, and they start fighting.

01:17:03.710 --> 01:17:07.538
It’s a Mother’s job, which is a thankless
job, absolute thankless job.

01:17:07.739 --> 01:17:11.308
I have to do it. And also only Mother can
do it. Because if you had Christ,

01:17:11.509 --> 01:17:14.350
He would have taken those eleven things
and finished off everyone.

01:17:14.550 --> 01:17:18.439
If you had asked Christ – Krishna - He had
also Samhara Shakti, He would have killed.

01:17:18.640 --> 01:17:22.558
But to use the whole thing with integrated
idea and with balancing,

01:17:22.759 --> 01:17:25.670
with understanding human beings you have
to have a Mother.

01:17:25.870 --> 01:17:29.230
And that’s why sometimes people try
to become very familiar

01:17:29.430 --> 01:17:36.562
and start taking advantage or taking
liberties, which is a wrong thing.

01:17:36.763 --> 01:17:42.481
Whatever I am I am and I’m Love -
I can’t help it.

01:17:42.682 --> 01:17:45.714
I really can’t help it. I’m Compassion.

01:17:45.915 --> 01:17:50.039
One day I did feel very disgusted, really.
Once I did feel very disgusted with people

01:17:50.240 --> 01:17:55.169
the way they were, and I was just saying
that “Forget it!”

01:17:55.370 --> 01:17:59.550
And then suddenly, I saw my photograph
and I saw my eyes,

01:17:59.750 --> 01:18:04.233
and I said, “Nirmala, you are Compassion,
you are Compassion, you can’t help it.

01:18:04.434 --> 01:18:07.150
YYou just can’t help it.” I have to work
it out.

01:18:07.351 --> 01:18:14.830
I know it means, it means sometimes too
much, too much, but I have to work it out.

01:18:15.030 --> 01:18:18.630
Now, some people come out with
a question, “Why You, Mother?”

01:18:18.854 --> 01:18:23.878
I said, “Why not you, it’s a good idea!
Come along and do it!”

01:18:24.079 --> 01:18:26.665
I’ll be the best - it will be the best
for me to retire,

01:18:26.866 --> 01:18:30.168
and my husband might give you a pension
for it, he’ll so happy

01:18:30.369 --> 01:18:32.606
that I’ve found out somebody who will
replace me.

01:18:32.807 --> 01:18:35.229
But I have not yet found out somebody
who will replace me,

01:18:35.430 --> 01:18:37.669
I wish you could, will be a good idea.

01:18:37.870 --> 01:18:41.083
Now, the name Nirmala itself is, means
Immaculate.

01:18:41.284 --> 01:18:46.731
Means, the one who is the cleansing power.
Is a name of the Goddess also.

01:18:46.932 --> 01:18:51.509
My, actually sign name is Lalita, is
the name of the Primordial Mother -

01:18:51.710 --> 01:18:56.269
that is the name of the Primordial Mother.

01:18:56.470 --> 01:19:00.889
But to be a human being with all these
centres around you working,

01:19:01.090 --> 01:19:04.368
for example for the last three days you
don’t know how much I am vibrating,

01:19:04.569 --> 01:19:08.185
you can ask Warren and other people,
I asked them to take the vibrations,

01:19:08.386 --> 01:19:10.339
and they were doing like this, where
they couldn’t touch me.

01:19:10.540 --> 01:19:13.949
They tried to put the hand on the head,
and they were just –

01:19:14.150 --> 01:19:17.870
and they didn’t know how to touch me,
even it is so much vibrating.

01:19:18.070 --> 01:19:22.909
So, it’s not easy to carry this, all this
load on this human body,

01:19:23.110 --> 01:19:26.052
appear like a human being, to act like
a human being,

01:19:26.253 --> 01:19:30.109
to behave like a human being, so that
there is a rapport.

01:19:30.310 --> 01:19:33.781
Why an Incarnation is needed? There
has to be a rapport,

01:19:33.982 --> 01:19:38.555
because the Unconscious cannot talk to you,
whatever you see in the dream

01:19:38.756 --> 01:19:42.084
comes back to you afterwards from
the subconscious area -

01:19:42.285 --> 01:19:49.990
all the ideas will be such a mess, such
a confusion and you cannot decide anything.

01:19:50.190 --> 01:19:56.709
So, it has to come on this earth as a human
being and tell you with a language.

01:19:56.910 --> 01:20:00.029
I never knew English all my life.

01:20:00.230 --> 01:20:03.629
So, first time I learnt English, but still
I don’t know American English.

01:20:03.830 --> 01:20:09.909
I hope I’ll be able to learn something more
when I travel around

01:20:10.110 --> 01:20:14.909
and it’s a thing that - it’s God’s desire
that you are to be realised.

01:20:15.110 --> 01:20:19.870
It’s all written in the Bible; it’s all
written in all the books of the scriptures.

01:20:20.070 --> 01:20:25.113
It is very largely written in the books
of Adi Shankaracharya,

01:20:25.314 --> 01:20:29.029
who had described me fully, in a very
full way.

01:20:29.230 --> 01:20:32.533
And it’s easy for Indians to get to me.

01:20:32.734 --> 01:20:37.411
I mean, though I have not much disciples
in the cities,

01:20:37.612 --> 01:20:41.070
but they are aware of my Advent and they
know that I am there.

01:20:41.271 --> 01:20:43.775
Most of them know about it.

01:20:43.976 --> 01:20:47.630
But they can’t understand why I have
come to America.

01:20:47.830 --> 01:20:53.142
They say that “Why do you come here?
The people here won’t accept You.”

01:20:53.343 --> 01:20:58.673
But I don’t think so, because I think you
are great seekers, very great seekers,

01:20:58.874 --> 01:21:03.229
born in this country - you are a special
type, and I have to work for you.

01:21:03.430 --> 01:21:08.961
I must say the transformation that has
taken place in the western sahaja yogis

01:21:09.162 --> 01:21:11.142
has not been achieved by Indians so much.

01:21:11.343 --> 01:21:13.950
Though they have an advantage because
they are born in a country

01:21:14.151 --> 01:21:17.916
which has basics, which keeps the attention
intact.

01:21:18.117 --> 01:21:22.140
The attention is very much intact. So,
it is easy to work it out there -

01:21:22.341 --> 01:21:24.846
here it is difficult, it doesn’t appeal
to people,

01:21:25.047 --> 01:21:29.142
but still, you are all great people,
so many of you are lost,

01:21:29.343 --> 01:21:33.310
but they can be all saved. But those
who are here should know

01:21:33.510 --> 01:21:37.436
that you have the greatest opportunity
in your lives today

01:21:37.637 --> 01:21:41.469
to be realised and to give realisation
to others.

01:21:41.670 --> 01:21:46.790
First of all, you have to become all right.
Then you can give light to others.

01:21:46.990 --> 01:21:52.538
Now, the greatest thing that is needed
for Sahaja Yoga is wisdom.

01:21:52.739 --> 01:21:57.237
And logically you will reach at
a conclusion and understand

01:21:57.438 --> 01:22:01.778
that Sahaja Yoga is the end of all
the problems of the world.

01:22:01.979 --> 01:22:06.229
Of all the problems of the world. For
example take the capitalism and communism.

01:22:06.430 --> 01:22:09.558
Now, I am a capitalist, because I have
all the powers,

01:22:09.759 --> 01:22:13.179
and I am the communist, because I cannot
enjoy it without giving it to you.

01:22:13.380 --> 01:22:16.012
But it’s spontaneous, I have not to do it

01:22:16.213 --> 01:22:19.990
because I think about it, it just works.
It is like that.

01:22:20.190 --> 01:22:23.207
All the problems: political problems,
economic problems -

01:22:23.408 --> 01:22:28.270
everything can be solved. Krishna has
said, “Yoga Kshema Vahamyaham.”

01:22:28.470 --> 01:22:32.694
“When you get your Yoga, you get your
well-being.” He has promised it.

01:22:32.895 --> 01:22:35.389
He could have said it, “Kshema Yoga
Vahamyaham.”

01:22:35.590 --> 01:22:39.755
He did not, he said, “Yoga Kshema
Vahamyaham.” First your yoga, first unite.

01:22:39.956 --> 01:22:43.029
Unite with the Spirit, then you are
blessed by all these things.

01:22:43.230 --> 01:22:47.843
This is the centre of even material wealth,
of Lakshmi, which works out.

01:22:48.044 --> 01:22:53.174
And all the sahaja yogis who have been to
me, are blessed by material wealth also,

01:22:53.375 --> 01:22:57.429
but not too much like Mister Ford - that’s
an extreme case, that’s a headache,

01:22:57.630 --> 01:23:03.430
but they get well-being from every angle,
in a balanced way and integrated way.

01:23:03.630 --> 01:23:07.789
So the last method is of integration - that
you get completely integrated.

01:23:07.990 --> 01:23:10.693
Whatever you do, your heart supports it,

01:23:10.894 --> 01:23:13.789
your mind supports it, and your body
supports it.

01:23:13.990 --> 01:23:18.240
You are completely integrated in one
being - that is your Spirit.

01:23:18.441 --> 01:23:19.430
May God bless you all.

01:23:19.630 --> 01:23:23.350
So, now this is the last lecture and I’m
going to Philadelphia,

01:23:23.550 --> 01:23:28.230
and you pray that Philadelphia people
get realisation more,

01:23:28.430 --> 01:23:34.190
and we get more people into Sahaj Yog,
and that they become enlightened.

01:23:34.390 --> 01:23:40.030
Then I’ll be going to Houston, then to
Los Angeles and Vancouver for a day.

01:23:40.231 --> 01:23:44.230
If you have any friends or relatives there
you can write to them,

01:23:44.430 --> 01:23:49.132
take the address, so that they contact
and they come down to the program.

01:23:49.333 --> 01:23:52.285
May God bless you all.

