01:24:09.350 --> 01:24:11.626
It’s better that you discover me than
I tell you,

01:24:11.827 --> 01:24:16.278
because Christ was crucified, everybody
was tortured.

01:24:16.479 --> 01:24:18.848
I do not want to hamper my work,

01:24:19.049 --> 01:24:22.644
because it makes no difference by telling
you anything before realisation.

01:24:22.845 --> 01:24:27.472
It’s better to tell you after realisation
that I am the Holy Ghost, no doubt.

01:24:27.673 --> 01:24:30.590
I am the one about which Christ has talked.

01:24:30.790 --> 01:24:37.350
I had told them, I had never said this
on - from a…

01:24:38.376 --> 01:24:42.695
[Yogini: “Platform”] platform, and I told,
they have been telling me,

01:24:42.896 --> 01:24:45.989
“Mother, You must say that once.”
I said, “In America I’ll declare it.”

01:24:46.190 --> 01:24:50.889
So, today I declare that I am the Holy
Ghost, I am the Holy Spirit,

01:24:51.090 --> 01:24:55.068
who has incarnated on this earth
for your realisation.

01:24:55.269 --> 01:24:58.053
May God bless you.

